          <h3>Eye Control AF</h3>
          <p>
            After calibration, you look at a subject and the camera focuses thereâ€”dramatically faster than joystick selection. The Dual Pixel CMOS AF II covers 100% of the frame with 1,053 zones. Tracking success rate exceeds 95%.
          </p>
